{"tid":398910,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"NGT48討論區第20回︰山口真帆生日倒數中!!!!","createTime":"2017-09-13T14:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T14:06:20.000Z","uid":46420,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b40b7e4f03fd5927ffa8e1503a93b3fcc5e5fbc5","tid":398910,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">溫馨提示</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我愛Aya,Aya愛我</span></span><br />\n<br />\nNGT48是日本一個由作詞家秋元康擔任製作人的女子偶像團體，主要的活動據點是日本北陸地方北端的主要城市新潟。2015年8月21日於新潟市歷史博物館正式公開，自此展開活動。NGT48的團名是以根據地新潟的羅馬音簡寫（羅馬拼音為NIIGATA），是AKB48第7個姊妹團體、以及第5個國內姊妹團體。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/tw21s5uj9/NGT_WORDS-new.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Ftw21s5uj9%2FNGT_WORDS-new.png&h=4b5f4e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/b5paOGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb5paOGf.jpg&h=92170641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1362pjmv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1362pjmv&h=6ef4f2e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"> NGT48 1st Anniversary - 好評發售中</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 這po有沒有版規?<br />\n無，我地好自由。不過請尊重成員及唔好人身攻擊其他會員。另外，新人加入時如有心儀的推請講低，方便大家討論。<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果討論其他48G姊妹團或46友團會否引起世界大戰？<br />\n絕對唔會，不用分哪麼細，錢都是肥秋賺。<br />\n<br />\n3. NGT有咩好歌推介?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn-iXRXpfVTs&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=20b0547f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n-iXRXpfVTs</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 如何開始支持NGT？<br />\n可以先翻看NGT番組《NGT48のにいがったフレンド!》（NGT48的新潟朋友）。每周一深夜12時59分在新潟TV（TeNY）播出。翻看方式請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 除了NGT48，有沒有其他推介？<br />\n<strong>SKE48 小畑優奈</strong><br />\n<img src=\"http://48pedia.org/images/f/f7/2017%E5%B9%B4SKE48%E3%83%97%E3%83%AD%E3%83%95%E3%82%A3%E3%83%BC%E3%83%AB_%E5%B0%8F%E7%95%91%E5%84%AA%E5%A5%88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F48pedia.org%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff7%2F2017%25E5%25B9%25B4SKE48%25E3%2583%2597%25E3%2583%25AD%25E3%2583%2595%25E3%2582%25A3%25E3%2583%25BC%25E3%2583%25AB_%25E5%25B0%258F%25E7%2595%2591%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%25A5%2588.jpg&h=38da9f2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/62ctadvm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F62ctadvm&h=14b1c30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lp8gua02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flp8gua02&h=915de326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nセンター︰荻野由佳<br />\n北原里英、本間日陽、中井りか、高倉萌香、柏木由紀、加藤美南、西潟茉莉奈、山口真帆、山田野絵、小熊倫実、太野彩香、長谷川玲奈、村雲颯香、菅原りこ、佐藤杏樹、宮島亜弥、角ゆりあ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">NGT48 公式 IG：<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/t7azu4rj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft7azu4rj&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f5be0ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/t7azu4rj</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">開 Po 用 Template:<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/rqye58ta\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frqye58ta&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=78f70a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/rqye58ta</a></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會員山本美優紀中譯48G歌曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://holland.pk/xs2k087y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxs2k087y&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d31878d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/xs2k087y</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舊po回帶：請參考 Template 文件下半部份</span></strong><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"70e9222160ef53ccd88ba92a46721431b5a4d458","tid":398910,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180c6ad58540f877e9f64d6ac66b7206e2e28b7f","tid":398910,"uid":35137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:02:08.000Z","msg":"1004"},{"pid":"40d0440b2b1dc6a620ee13ffbe7267a0a23afcf9","tid":398910,"uid":67331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:02:17.000Z","msg":"20？<br />\n回帶牙？"},{"pid":"15b2d64bd817fdebecb6b7644f143dfbba44d6e2","tid":398910,"uid":46420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v9pte51.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv9pte51.gif&h=18096799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/XfcrE7s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FXfcrE7s.gif&h=a92cb30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ov9jOOueBGtULeLmM/200w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ov9jOOueBGtULeLmM%2F200w.gif&h=3b990abe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3ohhwKPfIpQR7yzFZK/200w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3ohhwKPfIpQR7yzFZK%2F200w.gif&h=5c7f4a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請多多支持宮島亜弥<br />\n<br />\n🙇🙏🙇🙏🙇🙏🙇🙏"},{"pid":"4b03b5e10be74b24a6fc08fe8dc562d23572b464","tid":398910,"uid":52372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T14:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>20？<br />\n回帶牙？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10